data.description: Come see this cozy brick ranch in the established subdivision of Willowbrook. This home has many sought after features such as vaulted and beamed ceilings, a generous fenced in backyard, stainless steel appliances, a wood burning fireplace and no carpet, all without the muss and fuss of an HOA, There and many dining and shopping locations near and this home is a mere 2.5 miles away from the NWS.
